CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 28, 1953, pg. 17 reads: "Birthday Testimonial for Mrs. Robert L. Vann Is Tremendous!"
TitMainTitle: Men and women wearing evening wear, seated in ballroom of the Penn Sheraton with sunburst patterned curtains, Jessie Vann standing at microphone on far right, for Jessie Vann's birthday party
